---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Hummingbird Social Studio | Modern Wedding Template Design Studio"
  description="Learn about Hummingbird Social Studio, a modern wedding stationery template studio creating editable invitation suites, bridal shower invitations, signage, and celebration templates with a warm, polished feel."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container content">
      <p class="eyebrow">About the Studio</p>
      <h1>Thoughtful wedding templates with a warm, modern feel.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Hummingbird Social Studio creates editable wedding stationery templates
        for couples, hosts, and planners who want beautiful designs without the
        stress of starting from scratch.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Designed to feel personal</h2>
        <p>
          Wedding stationery should feel like part of the celebration, not just
          another task on the planning list. Each template is created with clean
          layouts, thoughtful spacing, warm color palettes, and easy-to-edit
          details so your final design feels polished and intentional.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Made for real-life planning</h2>
        <p>
          Digital templates give you flexibility. You can update names, dates,
          locations, wording, and details on your own timeline, then print at
          home, through a local print shop, or with an online printer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>A boutique studio feel</h2>
        <p>
          Hummingbird Social Studio is built around modern, romantic, and
          vintage-inspired stationery that feels elevated without feeling
          overly formal. The goal is simple: beautiful templates that are easy
          to use and easy to love.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="feature-band">
    <div class="container content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Style</p>
      <h2>Soft romance, modern structure, and a hint of nostalgia.</h2>
      <p>
        The studio’s design style blends romantic details with warm mid-century
        inspiration. Think refined typography, subtle vintage tones, playful
        shapes, simple layouts, and stationery that works beautifully across an
        entire event.
      </p>
      <p>
        From wedding invitations and bridal shower invites to menus, welcome
        signs, thank you cards, and day-of details, each piece is designed to
        help your celebration feel cohesive from the first invite to the final
        toast.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Wedding invitation suites</h3>
        <p>
          Coordinated invitation templates for modern weddings, intimate
          celebrations, destination events, and stylish gatherings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Bridal shower invitations</h3>
        <p>
          Editable shower templates with a polished, feminine, and modern feel
          for hosts who want something beautiful and easy to customize.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Day-of stationery</h3>
        <p>
          Menus, signage, seating charts, place cards, and finishing details
          that help create a cohesive guest experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why Templates?</p>
      <h2>Beautiful stationery should not feel complicated.</h2>
      <p>
        Wedding planning already comes with enough decisions. Editable templates
        make it easier to create coordinated stationery while still giving you
        control over the wording, timing, and final printed look.
      </p>
      <p>
        Instead of waiting on rounds of custom revisions, you can choose a
        design you love, personalize the details, and print when you are ready.
        It is a simple way to get a custom-feeling result without a fully custom
        process.
      </p>

      <div class="button-row">
        <a class="button" href="/how-it-works/">See How It Works</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/printing-guide/">Read the Printing Guide</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Need Something Custom?</p>
      <h2>Love the style but need a different layout?</h2>
      <p>
        If you like the Hummingbird Social Studio look but need a custom size,
        matching event piece, wording adjustment, or a more tailored stationery
        set, you can send a custom design request.
      </p>

      <div class="button-row">
        <a class="button" href="/custom-design-requests/">Request a Custom Design</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">Contact the Studio</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
